I"<p>Pauliana Valente Pimentel, 1975. Did the Photography course from the Gulbenkian Programme for Creativity and Artistic Creation. Was a member of the [Kameraphoto] collective. Has published several books and films. In 2015, received the Visual Arts Award from SPA. In 2016, was nominated for the NOVO BANCO Prize. Collaborates with international galleries. Her work is held in private and institutional collections, notably the Calouste Gulbenkian and EDP Foundation, MAAT, Novo Banco, and the Portuguese State Collection.</p>
